    @xray
    Scenario: Error 401 when sending the report to xray

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   The merged report directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/merged'
        And   The report test environment is not set
        And   'JIRA_XRAY_LOGIN' environment variable has been set to 'UNKNOWN_LOGIN'
        When  Xray Connector publishes test execution report to Xray
        Then  An execution error should be reported
        And   The error message should contain 'Error 401'

